## RelationType: 恢复数据源属于时间点副本

恢复数据源对象通过 timePointId 字段关联到时间点副本对象，表示该恢复数据源属于哪个时间点副本。

### Endpoint

| Source | Target | Type |
|--------|--------|------|
| recovery_datasource | timepoint_copy | direct |

### Mapping Rules

| Source Property | Target Property |
|-----------------|-----------------|
| timePointId | timePointId |
